  <abstract id="abstr_chi" date-changed="20091230" lang="chi" format="original">
    <p num="1">本实用新型是一种将胶片影像转换为数字资料的装置，包括有一主体、一架体、一底支架以及一底盖，其中架体结合在底支架的上部，整体容置在主体内，而底盖从下方组合封闭的。架体的上部设有一摄影镜头，底支架内设有一背光机构，而主体的两侧各设有一长槽，提供一胶片夹从一侧插入，所述的胶片夹可将胶片固设其内，并定位于背光机构的上方，利用摄影镜头取得胶片的影像，并转为数字资料，提供传输到另一电脑主机储存，达成快速将胶片上的影像转换为数字资料，便利于修改以及永久保存。</p>
  </abstract>
  <abstract id="abstr_eng" date-changed="20091230" lang="eng" format="original">
    <p>The utility model relates to a device used for switching film images to digital data, which comprises a main body, a frame body, a bottom support and a bottom cover, wherein the frame body is combined on the upper portion of the bottom support, and the whole body thereof is arranged in the main body, the bottom cover is combined closely from the lower portion, a camera lens is arranged on the upper portion of the support body, a backlight mechanism is arranged in the bottom support, a long groove is respectively arranged on each side of the main body, a film clip is inserted into the long grooves from one side, wherein film can be fixed in the film clip through the film clip, and can be located on the upper portion of the backlight mechanism, images can be obtained through the camera lens, and then the images are switched into digital data and can be transmitted and stored in the other host machine of a computer, thereby the rapid switching images on films to digital data is realized, and the device is convenient to alter and permanently store.</p>
  </abstract>
